{"tid":1571450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔撚係呀香港人","createTime":"2019-09-15T12:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T11:31:23.000Z","uid":124751,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e580825dd48988d8434631bc2a19c4a260f20bc","tid":1571450,"uid":124751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T12:16:13.000Z","msg":"我係今日出去發夢既手足<br />\n6半左右係灣仔比狗包抄 退左去跑馬地<br />\n銅鑼灣果陣都有好多狗 就行山路出番天后搭黨鐵<br />\n點知一落到柴灣方向月台就廣播話下一班不載客<br />\n班車一黎到成車都係畜龍 當時月台乜野人都有 <br />\n有手足 有普通人 個個都開始擔心<br />\n點知架車停低開左門 有一大班狗出左黎 無理到月台上既人<br />\n點知出完之後 入面有狗示意叫月台既人可以上車<br />\n月台上面90%撚樣入撚哂去<br />\n大佬你班人係咪傻撚左呀？？？？？<br />\n究竟你班港豬係咪仲未識驚？？<br />\n入到去困獸鬥咁 仲有人成個袋gear<br />\n為左快少少番去同班狗坐車？？<br />\n連象徵式杯葛下佢地都唔做？？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">玩左隻game成3個月啦醒少少啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8586a8b41f2dd30e95922040602bc1d58fa3c1f","tid":1571450,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T12:17:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span> <br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"a51fd6f23da2209970911a915663bae85ccb496b","tid":1571450,"uid":241276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:31:23.000Z","msg":"醒少少啦"}]}